@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.25 / v1 + 0.3)) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.15) * 0.18))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.54)
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.41)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((tmp + 0.61 * v0 + 0.45)))
    tmp = wp.exp((0.57 * v0))
    v1 = 0.34
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.08 / v2 + 0.05) / (v2 + 0.51 / tmp + 0.72)) * wp.exp((v2 + 0.07 - tmp + 0.49)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
